    "## Section 7: Testing Thread Continuity\n",
    "\n",
    "### pytest Fixtures for Webhook Payloads\n",
    "\n",
    "Thread continuity bugs are silent — they don't raise exceptions, they just send emails to the wrong thread. Testing must be explicit about asserting thread_id values.\n",
    "\n",
    "The tests below catch all three mistakes from Section 3 before they reach production."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "aa100028",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
